{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setMaximumAmbientCacheSize:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@NSUInteger","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSUInteger"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"cacheSize"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"withCompletionHandler:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"void","preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" (^)(","kind":"text"},{"text":"NSError","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSError","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" * ","kind":"text"},{"text":"error","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":")) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"completion","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":";","kind":"text"}],"platforms":["iOS"]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"cacheSize","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The maximum size in bytes for the ambient cache."}]}]},{"name":"completion","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The completion handler to call once the maximum ambient cache"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"size has been set. This handler is executed synchronously on the main queue."}]}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","text":"Discussion","anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method does not limit the space available to offline packs, and data in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offline packs does not count towards this limit. If you set the maximum ambient"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"cache size to 30 MB then download 20 MB of offline packs, 30 MB will remain"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"available for the ambient cache."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method should be called before the map and map style have been loaded."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This method is potentially expensive, as the database will trim cached data"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in order to prevent the ambient cache from being larger than the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"specified amount."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage\/setMaximumAmbientCacheSize:withCompletionHandler:"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOfflineStorage"]]},"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"title":"setMaximumAmbientCacheSize:withCompletionHandler:","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setMaximumAmbientCacheSize:withCompletionHandler:","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setMaximumAmbientCacheSize:withCompletionHandler:"}],"symbolKind":"method","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Instance Method","externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNOfflineStorage(im)setMaximumAmbientCacheSize:withCompletionHandler:"},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the maximum ambient cache size in bytes. The default maximum cache"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"size is 50 MB. To disable ambient caching, set the maximum ambient cache size"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"0"},{"type":"text","text":". Setting the maximum ambient cache size does not impact the maximum size"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of offline packs."}],"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnofflinestorage\/setmaximumambientcachesize:withcompletio